Take off--------------------------------------------------
Imagine:---
Imagine taking off of your love carrier by first time watching a girl taking off her cloths in front of you.
Hindi Meaning:---
nikaalna
When an aeroplane takes off, it leaves the ground and starts flying. (-land)
If you take time off, you obtain permission not to go to work for a short period of time.
Sentences:---
Can you take tomorrow off (from the office).
Lexicon!:---
3, 6, 7
